energy.usef.core.model

Class PlanboardMessage

  • java.lang.Object
    • energy.usef.core.model.PlanboardMessage

  • @Entity
public class PlanboardMessage
extends Object
    Entity class PlanboardMessage: This class is a representation of a PlanboardMessage. PlanboardMessage is unique for the combination: sequence, documentType and participantDomain. Except for the type: FLEX_ORDER_SETTLEMENT
